      "content": "Yeah, it sounds like it's gonna be a pretty big overhaul. The email said it's basically a \"personality reset\" to make sure all the AI writing tools under their umbrella sound the same. They're worried about the grit and the darker themes in your character arcs, so they want everything to be more PG and mainstream. It's mostly about brand consistency for them. I'm not sure how much control I have over it, it seems like it's just happening.",
